import React from "react";
import '../card/card.scss'
import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card';
import ListGroup from 'react-bootstrap/ListGroup';
import uxui from '../../img/uxui.png'
import { Fragment } from "react";

function Cards() {
  return (
    <Fragment className="cards-wrapper">
      <Card className="card" style={{ width: '25rem'}}>
      <Card.Img variant="top" src={uxui} />
      <Card.Body >
        <Card.Title>UI/UX Design</Card.Title>
        <Card.Text>
          Interpersonal skills - work better with others!
        </Card.Text>
      </Card.Body>
      <ListGroup className="list-group-flush">
        <ListGroup.Item>Tanah Air Team</ListGroup.Item>
        <ListGroup.Item>STARS</ListGroup.Item>
        <ListGroup.Item>$384</ListGroup.Item>
      </ListGroup>
    </Card>
      <Card className="card" style={{ width: '25rem'}}>
      <Card.Img variant="top" src={uxui} />
      <Card.Body >
        <Card.Title>UI/UX Design</Card.Title>
        <Card.Text>
          Interpersonal skills - work better with others!
        </Card.Text>
      </Card.Body>
      <ListGroup className="list-group-flush">
        <ListGroup.Item>Tanah Air Team</ListGroup.Item>
        <ListGroup.Item>STARS</ListGroup.Item>
        <ListGroup.Item>$384</ListGroup.Item>
      </ListGroup>
    </Card>
      <Card className="card" style={{ width: '25rem'}}>
      <Card.Img variant="top" src={uxui} />
      <Card.Body >
        <Card.Title>UI/UX Design</Card.Title>
        <Card.Text>
          Interpersonal skills - work better with others!
        </Card.Text>
      </Card.Body>
      <ListGroup className="list-group-flush">
        <ListGroup.Item>Tanah Air Team</ListGroup.Item>
        <ListGroup.Item>STARS</ListGroup.Item>
        <ListGroup.Item>$384</ListGroup.Item>
      </ListGroup>
    </Card>
    </Fragment>
  );
}

export default Cards;
